0k.<ref>{{cite news|last=Guyun|first=Jessica|title=Ellen DeGeneres selfie on Twitter is Oscar gold for Samsung|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2014/mar/03/business/la-fi-tn-ellen-degeneres-selfie-twitter-oscars-samsung-20140303|accessdate=April 16, 2014|work=Los Angeles Times|publisher=Tribune Publishing|date=March 3, 2014|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410203238/http://articles.latimes.com/2014/mar/03/business/la-fi-tn-ellen-degeneres-selfie-twitter-oscars-samsung-20140303|archivedate=April 10, 2014}}</ref>}}\n|-\n! 9\n| style=\"text-align:left; font-size:9pt;\" | \"\u300c100\u65e5\u5f8c\u306b\u6b7b\u306c\u30ef\u30cb\u300d100\u65e5\u76ee\" {{URL|https://twitter.com/yuukikikuchi/status/1240946299467259905}}<ref>{{cite tweet|author=\u304d\u304f\u3061\u3086\u3046\u304d|user=yuukikikuchi|number=1240946299467259905|date=March 20, 2020|title=\u300c100\u65e5\u5f8c\u306b\u6b7b\u306c\u30ef\u30cb\u300d100\u65e5\u76ee|accessdate=March 20, 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"left\" |Yuuki Kikuchi<br />@yuukikikuchi\n| 2.1\n| align=\"right\" | {{dts|March 20, 2020}}\n| {{efn-ua|Author \u304d\u304f\u3061\u3086\u3046\u304d(''Kikuchi Yuuki'') posted a [[Yonkoma manga|4-koma manga]] every day about a crocodile who dies after 100 days. This tweet was the last day.}}\n|-\n! 10\n| style=\"text-align:left; font-size:9pt;\" | \"how's self quarantine going?\" {{URL|https://twitter.com/iqraanabi/status/1239294114094632961}}<ref>{{cite tweet|author=Iqra Nabi|user=iqraanabi|number=1239294114094632961|date=March 16, 2020|title=\"how's self quarantine going?\"|accessdate=March 16, 2020}}</ref>\n| align=\"left\" |Iqra Nabi<br />@iqraanabi\n|2.0\n| align=\"right\" | {{dts|March 16, 2020}}\n| {{efn-ua|Iqra tweeted a video of her cat losing in a game of [[tic-tac-toe]], making light of the quarantine imposed during the [[2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic]].}}\n|-\n! 11\n| style=\"text-align:left; font-size:9pt;\" | \"\ud589\ubcf5\ud558\uac8c \ud574\uc8fc\uc154\uc11c \uac10\uc0ac\